    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the freedom sounds more like a burden tbh. if everything is just a choice between two neutral outcomes, then choosing the one that ends the suffering seems like the only logical conclusion. if there's no prize at the end, why keep playing a game you already know is rigged?",
